Leading your favourite team to victories is a wonderful experience. The gameplay can be very simple, merely strategising and handling the media but it can get complex and very taxing on time if one were to handle every single aspect of running a club. Alternatively, you can just delegate everything away and go on a prolonged holiday and pray for victory. This is a good title to purchase although it is unfortunate that Fifa did not sell its rights to this game maker, as a result you will not see authentic pictures of the players as well as logos of clubs. Nonetheless, this game is good and well worth buying.
