While presenting an extremely innovative and immersive experience of the football management appeal, it leaves gamers who are unfamiliar or rookie to the sport in the dark. Though the game is of high appeal to those who are well versed in the world of English football, one could easily advise those who are unfamiliar to steer away; this game is not for novices. This isn't to say that this lack of equality is a detraction from the game itself - quite the opposite - for those seasoned in English football, the game provides a beautiful experience for the hotseat of game management and requires extremely detailed choices for all aspects of the job in order to ensure success both on the field and off.
