Football manager 2015 is good improvement over its last version. Visual improvements are particularly very good. Game engine has improved, which is expected. New interface is very useful once you get accostom to it. Another thing that is improved is, Player interaction. Players are more and more interactive about transfer related issues like, selling young player or if player wants to leave, he make whole dressing room unhappy. All in all, they have improved the game but i was expecting more from FM on commentary,training improvements this time. So, bit disappointed in that sense. All in all latest FM version is always better than last one.
